data.eml:eml: Further records of non-cryptic New Zealand earthworms

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Blakemore, Robert (2011): Further records of non-cryptic New Zealand earthworms. ZooKeys 160: 23-46, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.160.2354, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.160.2354
